A wrapper for the U.S. Census Bureau APIs that returns data frames of Census data and metadata. Available datasets include the Decennial Census, American Community Survey, Small Area Health Insurance Estimates, Small Area Income and Poverty Estimates, Population Estimates and Projections, and more.

name: r-censusapi
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-censusapi
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/censusapi_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/censusapi/censusapi_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 554e967e7d7e2aa3272729d2a420d943b49c10aa3352ad5ab6178efae1a2a51a

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-rlang
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-rlang

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('censusapi')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('censusapi')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/hrecht/censusapi
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: A wrapper for the U.S. Census Bureau APIs that returns data frames of Census data and metadata. Available datasets include the Decennial Census, American Community Survey, Small Area Health Insurance Estimates, Small Area Income and Poverty Estimates, Population Estimates and Projections, and more.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - izahn
